Description: Quickly and easily submit your experimental workin 'R' to the 'PatentSafe' ELN
             from Amphora Research Systems. Support for this package is provided with your 
             PatentSafe support contract, so if you'd like assistance use
             the "Support" link on every PatentSafe page. 
